Der-Clang
=========

Submodules to build the Clang compiler


Building on Linux:

  cd Der-Clang
  ./update
  mkdir build
  cd build
  ./configure/llvm
  make -j9
  sudo make install


Building on Windows:

Call in the msysgit bash

  ./update

Open a Visual Studio command prompt and use cmake

  cd Der-Clang
  mkdir build
  cd build
  cmake ..\llvm

Open the .sln file and build.
